				<h4 id="syntax">
					Syntax
				</h4>
				<p>
					The syntax for the <mono>unwatch</mono> command is:
<div align="center">
<pre class="prettyprint inline lang-nift">
nsm unwatch dir (content-extension)
nsm unwatch dir (content-extension)
</pre>
</div>
				</p>

				<h4 id="description">
					Description
				</h4>
				<p>
					The <mono>unwatch</mono> command is for automatically tracking and untracking files based on the existence of content files in a specified directory. The default values for <mono>content-extension</mono> if none is provided is specified in the project configuration file <mono>.nsm/nift.config</mono>.
				</p>

				<h4 id="eg">
					Example
				</h4>
				<p>
					Example of <mono>watch</mono> being used:					

<div align="center">
<pre class="prettyprint inline linenums lang-nift">
nift unwatch content
nsm unwatch content/blog/posts ".md"</pre>
</div>
				</p>
